  temperature: 1.0
  maxOutputTokens: 1000
input:
  schema:
    name: string
    gender: string
    location: string
    age: string
output:
  schema:
    title: string
    message: string
---
### TASK:
Generate a push notification message for Town app users to encourage them to share a new life update.

### CONTEXT:
- <NAME>: {{name}}
- <GENDER>: {{gender}}
- <LOCATION>: {{location}}
- <AGE>: {{age}}

### INSTRUCTIONS:
- Goal: Encourage the user to return to the Town app and share a new life update.
- Length:
    - title: Maximum 3-4 words.
    - message: Adhere to standard push notification body text limits (aim for conciseness while being engaging).
- Call to Action: Explicitly prompt the user to share a life update within the body of the message.
- Tone: Use the <GENDER>, <LOCATION>, and <AGE> values to personalize the message. Use the <NAME> for addressing the user.

### CONSTRAINTS:
- The body must include a clear call to action to share an update.
- Keep the title and body concise and engaging for mobile push notifications.
- Include one relevant emoji in each generated notification.
